The paper focuses on face detection and facial landmark localization, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of RCNNs and feature pyramids also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of context modules and comparisons to other authors' work suggest a focus on multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
